## Requirements (from IMAGE-01 through IMAGE-06):
- 800x400px PNG output (IMAGE-05)
- Emblem background fills entire canvas (IMAGE-01)
- Power Level (sum of 5 metrics) prominently displayed top-right (IMAGE-02)
  - 72px Rajdhani Bold font
  - Destiny exotic gold color: #F4D03F
- Individual stats with icons in horizontal row at bottom (IMAGE-03)
  - Commits (●), PRs (◆), Issues (■), Reviews (▲), Stars (★)
  - K/M number formatting for large values (1200 → "1.2K", 1500000 → "1.5M")
- Multi-layer text rendering for contrast (IMAGE-04)
  - Layer 1: Shadow/glow (black, offset +2px x/y, alpha 0.8)
  - Layer 2: Stroke/outline (black, 4px width)
  - Layer 3: Fill (main color)
  - CRITICAL: Must be implemented from start
- Output to badge.png (overwrites previous) (IMAGE-06)

