## Bash script behavior to replicate:
- Reads data/emblem-config.json rotation array
- Uses ISO week number (YYYY-Www format, UTC)
- SHA256 hash of ISO week string → hex → decimal
- Modulo operation to select from rotation array
- Fallback emblem: 1409726931 (The Seventh Column)

## Files to create:
- internal/emblem/selector.go
